node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Rap by RAPTV on September 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'KISKA, "THE WORLD' LONELIEST ORCA" IS TRENDING AFTER A VIDEO OF HER BASHING HER HEAD ON GLASS IN AN ATTEMPT TO ESCAPE WENT VIRAL ON THE INTERNET'.

node.text: #Kiska, now known as “the world’s loneliest orca” in #marineland is trending after a video of her bashing her head on glass in an attempt to escape went viral on the internet. Kiska, who is now 44 years old, has spent the last 11 years of her life in captivity. The five calves that she gave birth to while at Marineland died at a young age, and her treatment at the the park has been called into question for many years while her mental and physical health visibly deteriorate. With the amount of light currently being shed on this topic, we are hoping this orca can be freed as soon as possible. #FREEKISKA
